{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"6702a43a-5473-44d7-a720-1ba774e226a1","content":"This template is **not quite ready** to publish. Key issues:\n\n1. **Missing `$schema`** — Add `\"$schema\": \"http://json.schemastore.org/template\"` for tooling validation.\n2. **Missing `groupIdentity`** — Recommended for NuGet so multiple versions/variants are grouped correctly.\n3. **Missing `precedence`** — Needed if you plan to ship updates; helps the engine pick the latest template.\n4. **Missing `preferNameDirectory`** — Usually set to `true` for project templates.\n5. **No `description`** — NuGet listing will look bare without a template description.\n6. **`sourceName` unused check** — Ensure your project files/namespaces actually use `MyWebApi` so the rename works.\n\nThe structure and required fields (`identity`, `name`, `shortName`, `author`, `tags`) are present and valid, so it's *functional*—but adding the above will make it production-quality for NuGet.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"eb035f12-468e-46c9-bed4-c3d4b75765a5","outputTokens":231,"requestId":"7830:F7FBE:B7325D:D53323:69F3FC36"},"id":"67565d16-8a91-49c5-a26c-a42550758cf5","timestamp":"2026-05-01T01:05:02.614Z","parentId":"bfa5bd89-b18c-4c20-8f74-a695e9b5133a"}
